Privacy Policy
At Sadi Tech / eClixTech, we respect your privacy and value our relationship with you. This Privacy Policy outlines how we handle your information and ensure your data privacy.
What data we collect
When you use the Ovulation Tracker & Calculator App, we may collect:
Device Information:
Device type, operating system, and unique identifiers, purely for technical purposes and app functionality.
How we use your data
Your data is primarily used to:
Ensure proper functioning of the app on your device.
Improve app performance and user experience.
We do not store or use any health data or personal identifiers within the app. All data related to menstrual cycles, symptoms, and other related details remain on your device and are not accessed, processed, or stored by us.
Lawful bases for processing
Our basis for processing your limited data is **legitimate interests**; specifically, ensuring the app functions correctly on your device.
Data Sharing
We do not share any data with third parties. All data remains on your device and is not transmitted or stored externally.
Data Retention
Given that we do not store any user data, there is no data retention period applicable to our app. All information remains on the user's device until the app is uninstalled or the data is deleted by the user.
Your Rights
Under the GDPR, you have the right to:
Request information about whether we hold personal data about you.
Request correction of incorrect or incomplete data.
Request deletion of your personal data.
Object to processing of your personal data.
Request restriction of processing your personal data.
Request transfer of your personal data.
Data Security
We prioritize your data's protection and have implemented measures to ensure your data's security on your device. Our app does not have any backend servers or cloud storage, ensuring your data's utmost privacy.
Changes to this policy
We may update this policy from time to time. When we do, we'll notify users via app updates or other appropriate means.
Contact Us
